"{\"uid\": \"dailycaller.com-2024-08-09-olympic-committee-president-suggests-theres-no-scientific-way-to-differentiate-between-men-and-women\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"(Photo by Alex Broadway/Getty Images)  International Olympic Committee (IOC) President Thomas Bach suggested there is no scientific way to differentiate between men and women during a press conference on Friday.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 211, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 10, \"end\": 14, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Rousseau\", \"score\": 0.9999995371518869, \"rank\": 2.821519592650103e-07, \"text\": \"Alex\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Rousseau\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Rousseau\"}, {\"begin\": 15, \"end\": 23, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Broadway_theatre\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.185937744716295e-21, \"text\": \"Broadway\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Broadway_theatre\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Broadway_theatre\"}, {\"begin\": 24, \"end\": 29, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Getty_Images\", \"score\": 0.9999999967319582, \"rank\": 2.7016417394628063e-09, \"text\": \"Getty\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Getty_Images\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Getty_Images\"}, {\"begin\": 39, \"end\": 76, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee (IOC)\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 87, \"end\": 98, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Bach\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Thomas Bach\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Bach\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Bach\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sex eligibility rules have been a point ofcontentionat the 2024 Paris Olympics, with Italian boxer Angela Carini withdrawing just 46 seconds into her fight with Algerian fighter Imane Khelif.\", \"from\": 213, \"to\": 404, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 298, \"end\": 305, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_language\", \"score\": 0.9964686727073379, \"rank\": 0.00199710959860312, \"text\": \"Italian\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_language\"}, {\"begin\": 312, \"end\": 325, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\", \"score\": 0.9999962103662667, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Angela Carini\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\"}, {\"begin\": 374, \"end\": 382, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"score\": 0.9886109848370693, \"rank\": 0.009508214407050143, \"text\": \"Algerian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\"}, {\"begin\": 391, \"end\": 403, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"score\": 0.9999996421623295, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Imane Khelif\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Perhaps as a result, Bach was asked Friday if the committee would perform a review of its sex change guidelines, in response to which he stated there was no concrete, scientific way to differentiate men from women.\", \"from\": 405, \"to\": 619, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 426, \"end\": 430, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johann_Sebastian_Bach\", \"score\": 0.9999617121215502, \"rank\": 3.828934452131357e-05, \"text\": \"Bach\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johann_Sebastian_Bach\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johann_Sebastian_Bach\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We have said from the very beginning, if somebody presented us [a] scientifically solid system how to identify men and women we [the IOC] are the first ones to do it,\\\" Bach told reporters.\", \"from\": 621, \"to\": 810, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 755, \"end\": 758, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.59552666198497e-16, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 790, \"end\": 794, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johann_Sebastian_Bach\", \"score\": 0.9999617121215502, \"rank\": 3.828934452131357e-05, \"text\": \"Bach\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johann_Sebastian_Bach\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johann_Sebastian_Bach\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It is not as easy as some in this cultural world may want to portray it - that the XX or the XY [chromosome] is the clear distinction between men and women.\\\"\", \"from\": 811, \"to\": 969, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 895, \"end\": 897, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/XY_sex-determination_system\", \"score\": 0.9999999484946342, \"rank\": 5.150533734588156e-08, \"text\": \"XX\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/XY_sex-determination_system\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/XY_sex-determination_system\"}, {\"begin\": 905, \"end\": 907, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phenotype\", \"score\": 0.5606409664000102, \"rank\": 0.7836724387540128, \"text\": \"XY\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phenotype\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phenotype\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"WATCH:    Strap a dunce cap on this guy and give him the old point and laughhttps://t.co/7AA0jj59ca  - Vince Coglianese (@VinceCoglianese)August 9, 2024    As of now, testosterone level - not whether someone has an XX or XY chromosomal pattern - is the key criterion in Olympic eligibility, NBC Newsreported.\", \"from\": 971, \"to\": 1279, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1055, \"end\": 1059, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Twitter\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"t.co\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Twitter\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Twitter\"}, {\"begin\": 1186, \"end\": 1188, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/XY_sex-determination_system\", \"score\": 0.9999999484946342, \"rank\": 5.150533734588156e-08, \"text\": \"XX\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/XY_sex-determination_system\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/XY_sex-determination_system\"}, {\"begin\": 1192, \"end\": 1194, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phenotype\", \"score\": 0.5606409664000102, \"rank\": 0.7836724387540128, \"text\": \"XY\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phenotype\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phenotype\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Bach also suggested climate change could affect the timing of future Olympics during the Friday press conference,accordingto Sports Illustrated (SI).\", \"from\": 1281, \"to\": 1430, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1281, \"end\": 1285, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johann_Sebastian_Bach\", \"score\": 0.9999617121215502, \"rank\": 3.828934452131357e-05, \"text\": \"Bach\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johann_Sebastian_Bach\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johann_Sebastian_Bach\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"If the climate change is continuing in a way that the experts are forecasting it, then it will be very difficult to organize Olympic Games in summer, in August,\\\" Bach said, according to SI.\", \"from\": 1432, \"to\": 1622, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1595, \"end\": 1599, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johann_Sebastian_Bach\", \"score\": 0.9999617121215502, \"rank\": 3.828934452131357e-05, \"text\": \"Bach\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johann_Sebastian_Bach\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johann_Sebastian_Bach\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The IOC president's comments come after the 2024 Paris Olympics opening ceremony starred drag queensposingas Christian imagery, including \\\"The Last Supper.\\\"\", \"from\": 1624, \"to\": 1780, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1628, \"end\": 1631, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.59552666198497e-16, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 1733, \"end\": 1742, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.6661555181500672, \"rank\": 0.3974430336959483, \"text\": \"Christian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"All content created by the Daily Caller News Foundation, an independent and nonpartisan newswire service, is available without charge to any legitimate news publisher that can provide a large audience.\", \"from\": 1782, \"to\": 1983, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1809, \"end\": 1821, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Daily_Caller\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"